---
title: Coconut Caribbean Chicken & Rice Bowl with Rainbow Slaw & Peanuts
description: Caribbean spiced chicken is such a party for your mouth, we had to step up every element of this lively dish. From the rainbow slaw to the crunchy peanuts, each colourful bite is a delight!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
